divs: Sighting Detailsi walked out my back door saw 2 bright objects to the south east hovering over downtown binghamton, when i walked out more to get a better look i noticed there wre more, at least 4 maybe 5 bright orange objects. As the clouds became thicker they started vanishing, before they were gone i saw on of the objects move from left right approaching one of the other lights, then one by one they all just vanished, the entire thing only lasted a few minutes and i had 3 witnesses with me at the time. i attempted to get video but it was too dark for my camera to see them.
